title: The Million Dollar Sticky
description: Contestants answer questions to get to the Cube of Cash. Any money that sticks to their gooey body, they get to take home!
quote: Are you ready to get sticky with Micky?
altHero: host Mickey with cash stuck to his palms
alt1: two women paint honey on a contestant
alt2: the contestant giggles as they brush honey on his neck
alt4: honey contestant in a glass box with money flying around and sticking to his body
